title: Home Brewing: A Complete Guide On How To Brew Beer
description:
In this book, you get... 
1. A step by step guide that makes your first homebrew easy and fun. 
2. Over 350 pages of information that sets you apart from 
amateur brewers. 
3. 13 amazing recipes of various styles and flavors. 
4. A profound list of the best equipment, websites, calculators, 
forums, brewing apps, recipes, and tons more! 
5. A robust list of trouble shooting tips
